Malice/ Hellplague:

Malice was sitting in a chair, feeling so miserable he could be 
extinguished right there and then.  He almost ignored Rodimus, but 
felt he had to answer.

"What is it, Rodimus?" he asked in a dull tone.

Hellplague received the coordinates and radioed to Celeron.

"Follow me, we are going to take a slight detour."
